I Love Healthy Fresh! My daughter and I often purchase lunch or dinner from healthy fresh whenever we aren't in the mood to cook, scrambling up a sandwich or mix a mere salad. We have tried numerous items on the menu and never have we been dissatisfied. They fruit and vegetables are always fresh. Their hot and cold sandwich are always fresh and staked nicely. Healthy fresh also makes the very smoothies. Though I never post reviews or ratings this review is well deserved, before today I would have rated them with ☆☆☆☆'s. Today I was in the mood for some healthy fresh... therefore I called in an order. Once I was made aware that my delivery had arrived, I gathered my money. To make a long story a tab but short I ended up giving my delivery person ☆Candito☆ $20.00 to much for said order. I did not realize that I overpaid by $20.00 until after 2 or 3 hours had passed by. I called healthy fresh some to the young that is always very pleasant whenever I call and she told me to hold the line.  When she returned she said the delivery person had the money, but had not handed in his delivery monies at that point. He had not checked and that my money was still folded up in his pocket the same exact way that I gave it to him. She said he had one more order to deliver, then he'll bring you the overpayment. Thirty (30) minutes later he was ringing my phone.  Money was still shoved down in his fanny pack. 🤑🙂SO NOT ONLY DOES HEALTHY FRESH HAVE SOME OF THE FRESHEST FOOD ON THIS SIDE OF TOWN... BUT THEY ALSO HAVE SOME GREAT INTEGRITY 👍🤑 Side note: Yes I did tip💵 him! ☆☆☆☆☆'s
